branchCategory.description:
&lt;p&gt;
SMC&apos;s updated VXD series for oil (viscosity not exceed 50mm&#xb2;/s) is a pilot operated, 2 port solenoid valve. The renewed VXD is not only smaller, but uses less power compared to the previous version. Available in brass and stainless steel, the VXD series also offers low concentration ozone resistant and oil free options. Flow rate ranges from Cv of 1.9 to 49
&lt;/p&gt;

